Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:45.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard’s finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima’s returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you’ve been jilted…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:32.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:36.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know there’s no place for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:45.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Harima?\NAre you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:47.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you turned into a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were quick…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to eat a\Nhome-made lunch that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:32.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from the bottom of hell\Njust to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:34.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san’s heart is already mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never forgive those like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,who use wicked techniques\Nto steal people’s hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:04.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad… Until a little while ago,\Nyou ruled this campus…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing your dear Tsukamoto-san\Nand being tormented by me…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:13.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end you were driven to the ends\Nof the earth. That is just too miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I pity you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle hasn’t ended yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:25.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take back Tenma-chan\Nand the peace of the campus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You never give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you, Karasuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How… did you become… so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:05:00.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grief… Grief changed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have… lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:26.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan, the villains are gone.\NEverything will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… actually… Actually, Harima-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:38.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s alright. It’s alright.\NThat’s all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can live for the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I do too.
