Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:11.23,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:17.11,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:26.30,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:33.14,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:41.96,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:49.19,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:56.60,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsteadily mustering strength, I want to try diving into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:03.77,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:13.22,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly floating, again today I am alone above the clouds
