Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:52.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Karasuma-kun, are the\Nrice balls a little too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Karasuma-kun,\Ndoes it taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:12.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m enjoying this,\Nbut is it boring for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a masterpiece…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s quite good for a first effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did you\Ndecide to write a manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:46.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No… no… It’s alright!\NIf you don’t want to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well… Then, why did you bring it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:55.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I’m a big fan of Nijou-sensei, whose work are published in your magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true, there is an influence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you drew the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:04.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there? I thought so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if that’s the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:09.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s going to be a New Face Award\Nin the next Jo Nijou Awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:14.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nijou-sensei will be a special judge.\NWhy don’t you submit this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you could at least\Nget an honorable mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you win the new faces award,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,the next step is to aim\Nfor a serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re still young.\NYou needn’t be impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:32.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nijou-sensei’s work certainly encouraged me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:38.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That writer saved me. I aimed\Nfor him when I wrote this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got really excited by his\N“Genroku Self-defense Force” myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It was the same for me! No wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:50.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who produced that work\Nknows what it’s about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They go into enemy territory only\Nto find it extremely peaceful…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no reason for them\Nto go there at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Ah, that was really popular, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:04.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Nijou-sensei just arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming by, Nijou-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then… I’ll keep this…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?! Hey!
