Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.50,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Café El Cado
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s raining hard, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just a shower, so it’ll end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san’s face remains slack…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t hide it. Don’t hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently you’ve been\Nconversing with Karasuma-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it looks like you’re getting cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How? Why? How come you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t take much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:14.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. What are you doing\Nout in the rain like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was… a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:45.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The last road left for me to take…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing a manga…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:51.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And becoming a little famous…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:55.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere, she… that girl I once loved…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She would by chance, pick up my book\Nin the corner of a book store…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,“Strange,” she’d say, smiling a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:07.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that… would have made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, looking closely,\Nyou’re really young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:22.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll catch a cold.\NYou have nowhere to go, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my place, ah, what’s your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:31.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My pen name is Hario Harima so that the\Nkids would think it funny and remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:36.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I wonder about\Nrice balls every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:40.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are rice balls Karasuma-kun’s favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure he’s not just enduring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:48.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right, Karasuma-kun said he liked curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:53.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s it, Karasuma-kun felt sorry\Nfor me because I was so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t I notice all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:02.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry! I was depending\Non his kindness! I’m so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:07.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, tomorrow, I’ll go back to the\Nbeginning and ask Yakumo to make curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Men like home cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:15.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get to a man’s heart,\Nfood is the best bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can’t cook…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it’s bad, if you put\Nyour love in it, that’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You’re right. If it’s love,\Nno one can beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I’ll try home-made curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:54.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, when I first\Nsaw you, something went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re just the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also jilted a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Men’s clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:36.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m out of beer, and I don’t\Nhave much cash this month…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped. I’ll just have\Nto make do with low-malt beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. You’re a minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:50.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not what I mean. I need\Nstronger alcohol to get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:12.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… so in the end, I was just\Nwrestling with myself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:18.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A small but warm home with two children…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:22.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,On her birthday, I’d secretly\Nget champagne and flowers ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:27.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was all a fleeting dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing This is piece of trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The manuscript was destroyed like my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:53.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fall in love many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:58.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,For example… Right now,\Nright in front of your eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N… No… I’m…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:13.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? That was unreasonable,\Nwasn’t it? Don’t let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,To Hario Harima-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:58.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I read your manga.\NIt was very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:03.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have talent.\NYou shouldn’t quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy yourself some food\Nwith this 1000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:13.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… I can’t take this money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m already in her debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,After she said she was\Nshort on cash this month…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s more…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:25.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not as good as Nijou-sensei’s\N“Genroku Self-defense Force” though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a fan.
