Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients are all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, are you sure you can do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m fine! I’m fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no meaning\Nif I don’t do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:54.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You take it easy and\Nwatch TV or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! I cut my finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the bandages!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see… Next is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, put the meat in\Nbefore the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo, the fire extinguisher,\Nthe fire extinguisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:20.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bro, see you here a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well… Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry made with love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:33.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, let’s give it a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never tasted anything like it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:49.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad you’re here.\NIori, taste this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:53.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat, Shin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:01.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pancakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:02.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the third day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:10.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hario, I left lunch money\Non the table, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:21.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I said, in the end\NI keep returning to that woman’s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:26.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you?\NWhere did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:39.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:49.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all places, we just had to run into each other here at the edge of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:52.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you won’t find me\Nthe way I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:01.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not the Kenji Harima\Nyou know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:07.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve fallen as far as I can go\Nand my hair has fallen out on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want you to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s better for both of us\Nif we just pass each other by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Tenma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:17.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:23.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori,  Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Tenma-chan’s pet cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s being washed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:34.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I mustn’t have anything more to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Someone! Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:41.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save him! Please save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else will save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone’s jumped in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:29.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan, look at how\NI’ve changed and laugh at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:32.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you… Could you possibly be… Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A kappa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:36.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Sanpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kappa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:54.33,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:00.09,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.79,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:10.26,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:14.88,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:17.55,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:20.94,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:23.79,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:28.23,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:31.37,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.56,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:40.57,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.58,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.49,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:50.47,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:07.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma’s feeding him rice balls again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:08.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She just doesn’t learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:10.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she messed up the curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:12.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s only one thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:13.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:15.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on School Rumble:
