Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the signs don’t say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:19.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
